{"tid":1514744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你地話有錢出錢嘅，同我入黎。蘋果：一齊撐學生訂閱計劃","createTime":"2019-08-29T01:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T04:10:51.000Z","uid":196345,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"86879affd65cbac8b6ad40683006d7fa102ce161","tid":1514744,"uid":196345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T01:03:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e08UdJG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe08UdJG.jpg&h=f19d6f48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190828/59979353\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190828%2F59979353&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTDBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=ec594c17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190828%2F59979353&h=a099d9e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190828/59979353</a><br />\n<br />\n同學們不但關心時事，更熱切為香港人發聲。惟我們了解尚未踏足社會的同學們，未必能夠負擔訂閱費用，為了讓他們能夠以不同角度緊貼社會局勢，現推出「撐學生訂閱計劃」，讓他們能夠不用分毫，盡覽《蘋果動新聞》和台灣《蘋果新聞網》所有新聞及精采內容，鼓勵有心人為學生加油，讓學生免費閲覽《蘋果》，共同擁抱香港核心價值，一起守護我城！"},{"pid":"ab6581ac491a5106f87c0e90f67fb9347def840d","tid":1514744,"uid":250444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T01:03:57.000Z","msg":"屌 你哋係咪誤解左兄弟爬山嘅意思<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1514726\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1514726</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c45f40e46a47d97f92da31d78ceb91726dced1e6","tid":1514744,"uid":60924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T01:08:58.000Z","msg":"一年300蚊，蘋果捱唔捱到架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7807e584ea8eb497b75b697a1532c21b55860da2","tid":1514744,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT